{c_label}Cooldown:{/c} {c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Subo places a concussive trap that arms after {c_number}[{SF_9}|1|]{/c} |4second;seconds. When an enemy moves within range, it explodes for {if:SF_24}{c_number}{payload:TRAP_DAMAGE}{/c}{else}moderate{/if} Physical damage and Stuns enemies for {c_number}[{SF_11}|1|]{/c} |4second;seconds.

Selecting a Mercenary Core Skill alters their wielded Weapon and Basic Attack.
{c_label}Weapon:{/c} {c_important}Bow{/c}
{c_label}Basic Attack:{/c} {c_important}Heavy Shot{/c}
Subo fires a toughened arrow at an enemy, dealing {if:SF_24}{c_number}{payload:MELEE_PAYLOAD_TOOLTIP}{/c}{else}moderate{/if} Physical damage with a {c_number}[{SF_16}*100|%|]{/c} chance to Stun for {c_number}[{SF_17}|1|]{/c} |4second;seconds.
